{"tid":1624170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路障應該係噉set","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:34:33.000Z","uid":40855,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bf29b169fe7d0fe98d89234bfd1c989c404448fa","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"而家唔係打陣地戰嘅時候，傳統路障只能夠短暫阻止到班差佬推進，當佢哋將雜物推翻去兩邊，成條路就暢通無阻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uEUOL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uEUOL.jpg&h=1e47f274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今時今日嘅路障，目的係<span style=\"color: red;\">阻礙</span>而唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">阻擋</span>，唔係打陣地戰，無人喺路障後面開槍丟手榴彈，巨型路障作用有限。<br />\n<br />\n反而應該將雜物散落一地，包括行人路，噉先阻礙到對方推進，或者將路障延長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8hZUP7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8hZUP7.png&h=c0d9ee3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSRLQo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSRLQo9.jpg&h=fa773363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網絡圖片，1004元朗）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3sEp5Xv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3sEp5Xv.jpg&h=feba65eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網絡圖片，1004土瓜灣）<br />\n<br />\n當然，傳統路障可以set，但最前方就夠，之後喺預計對方進軍路線（如連接狗屋嘅幹道）將障礙物散滿一地。"},{"pid":"2de03532d4cfa38dbc4d701c0ad1551beb049e1e","tid":1624170,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:09:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ccfc6dbf8a2e81c0bdd1f3a0cfd888e61491f11","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fa30bd03a63c1e54d2e7273afadf3e383bbbccda","tid":1624170,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7ad79a73de89b1017ae82b89640e943c75c023","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2de03532d4cfa38dbc4d701c0ad1551beb049e1e","tid":1624170,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:09:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"暫時隔一兩晚十八區暴動都可以"},{"pid":"00b56c3304b2093502db16d665491c64a55a8d35","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:38:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"aeac40f17b54432c61c77269d5a2e18a5456adde","tid":1624170,"uid":140726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">狗狗真係好驚快閃行動<br />\n班狗平時喺連登行動post/TG收風早定部署<br />\n一轉快閃模式佢地已經失去行動方向<br />\n佢地好驚小team行動好驚俾人圍<br />\n所以班狗要時間部署集結好先一齊行動<br />\n遊行完請唔好戀戰<br />\n各散去各區做快閃</span>"},{"pid":"1104a0541babdce96601a4d8de91eb7b50677896","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"016acd4b6eca14f205c12fdea63559d0340e1beb","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e7bb2bb3f28c575c6310913aa136e32a2cb52a40","tid":1624170,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:14:04.000Z","msg":"縱深的重要性大家終於知"},{"pid":"e4bdadc18563770a555fbdb8acfbdd81bf5e2525","tid":1624170,"uid":44117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"362209bbb91232442c5f4df334855cf8088f6560","tid":1624170,"uid":203598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f59095276ef9a18c0bbaf2e0f20b468d23959f6f","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c15c404c0fd26c9474e83bc54ca19a7b96e8a9ea","tid":1624170,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":